P_HTM[181]='*Vinā vitakkavicārehi assāsapassāsānaṃ uppādakkhaṇe tesaṃ vacīsaṅkhāro nuppajjati, no ca tesaṃ kāyasaṅkhāro nuppajjati. Sabbesaṃ cittassa bhaṅgakkhaṇe vinā assāsapassāsehi avitakkaavicāracittassa uppādakkhaṇe nirodhasamāpannānaṃ asaññasattānaṃ tesaṃ vacīsaṅkhāro ca nuppajjati kāyasaṅkhāro ca nuppajjati.*';
