P_HTM[186]='*Vinā vitakkavicārehi cittassa uppādakkhaṇe tesaṃ vacīsaṅkhāro nuppajjati, no ca tesaṃ cittasaṅkhāro nuppajjati. Sabbesaṃ cittassa bhaṅgakkhaṇe nirodhasamāpannānaṃ asaññasattānaṃ tesaṃ vacīsaṅkhāro ca nuppajjati cittasaṅkhāro ca nuppajjati.*';
