P_HTM[3762]='*(11) Atītānāgatavāro*';
P_HTM[3763]='*101. (Ka) yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjittha no ca taṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ, taṃ cittaṃ uppajjissatīti? No.*';
P_HTM[3764]='*(Kha) yaṃ vā pana cittaṃ uppajjissati no ca taṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ, taṃ cittaṃ uppajjitthāti? No.*';
P_HTM[3765]='*(Ka) yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjittha no ca taṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjissatīti? Āmantā.*';
P_HTM[3766]='*(Kha) yaṃ vā pana cittaṃ na uppajjissati no ca taṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjitthāti? Āmantā.*';
P_HTM[3767]='*(12) Uppannuppajjamānavāro*';
P_HTM[3768]='*102. (Ka) uppannaṃ  uppajjamānanti?*';
P_HTM[3769]='*Bhaṅgakkhaṇe uppannaṃ, no ca uppajjamānaṃ. Uppādakkhaṇe uppannañceva uppajjamānañca.*';
P_HTM[3770]='*(Kha) uppajjamānaṃ uppannanti? Āmantā.*';
P_HTM[3771]='*(Ka) na uppannaṃ na uppajjamānanti? Āmantā.*';
P_HTM[3772]='*(Kha) na uppajjamānaṃ na uppannanti?*';
P_HTM[3773]='*Bhaṅgakkhaṇe na uppajjamānaṃ, no ca na uppannaṃ. Atītānāgataṃ cittaṃ na ceva uppajjamānaṃ na ca uppannaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3774]='*(13) Niruddhanirujjhamānavāro*';
P_HTM[3775]='*103. (Ka) niruddhaṃ nirujjhamānanti? No.*';
P_HTM[3776]='*(Kha) nirujjhamānaṃ niruddhanti? No.*';
P_HTM[3777]='*(Ka) na niruddhaṃ na nirujjhamānanti?*';
P_HTM[3778]='*Bhaṅgakkhaṇe na niruddhaṃ, no ca na nirujjhamānaṃ. Uppādakkhaṇe anāgatañca cittaṃ na ceva niruddhaṃ na ca nirujjhamānaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3779]='*(Kha) na nirujjhamānaṃ na niruddhanti?*';
P_HTM[3780]='*Atītaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhamānaṃ, no ca na niruddhaṃ. Uppādakkhaṇe anāgatañca cittaṃ na ceva nirujjhamānaṃ na ca niruddhaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3781]='*(14) Atikkantakālavāro*';
P_HTM[3782]='*104. (Ka) yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ taṃ cittanti?*';
P_HTM[3783]='*Bhaṅgakkhaṇe cittaṃ uppādakkhaṇaṃ  vītikkantaṃ bhaṅgakkhaṇaṃ avītikkantaṃ, atītaṃ cittaṃ uppādakkhaṇañca vītikkantaṃ bhaṅgakkhaṇañca vītikkantaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3784]='*(Kha) yaṃ vā pana cittaṃ nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ taṃ cittanti?*';
P_HTM[3785]='*Atītaṃ cittaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3786]='*(Ka) yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, na nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ taṃ cittanti?*';
P_HTM[3787]='*Uppādakkhaṇe anāgataṃ cittaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3788]='*(Kha) yaṃ vā pana cittaṃ na nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, na uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ taṃ cittanti?*';
P_HTM[3789]='*Bhaṅgakkhaṇe cittaṃ bhaṅgakkhaṇaṃ avītikkantaṃ no ca uppādakkhaṇaṃ avītikkantaṃ, uppādakkhaṇe anāgatañca cittaṃ bhaṅgakkhaṇañca avītikkantaṃ uppādakkhaṇañca avītikkantaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3790]='*1. Suddhacittasāmañña*';
P_HTM[3791]='*3. Puggaladhammavāro*';
